{
  "stem": "21626.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I opened it far too often and far too clearly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And unknown to me, of course, our room was bugged.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My office was bugged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And before I knew where I was, I found myself being interrogated and held for about three days and three nights.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I didn't know what it was about.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Before they did that, I had a-- I befriended an American businessmen who traveled through Europe on occasions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he wanted to marry me, but I didn't want to marry him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And whenever he came to Prague, you know, we had dinner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I helped him, if he bought anything, to parcel the things up and that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when I was interrogated, they knew my every move.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had my every letter over the last three months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I couldn't understand why people from the West weren't writing to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They had all my correspondence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I learned only later that they assumed that I was giving inform-- they knew there was a leak of information.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they assumed it was I, because they knew my beliefs and my aversion to communism.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they thought that this American Joe was the one that I was passing the information to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So luckily for me, they found out who the culprit was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was my boss, and he was shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was told if that hadn't happened, I would have been sent to Siberia, to the mines, on suspicion only.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had a very lucky escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that scared the living daylights out of me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after that, I did my utmost to get myself a passport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because after the communists took over, normal passports were no longer valid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And to get back to Britain or to Israel-- I applied for visas to both the places.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
